name: Oksana X
description: Love to laugh. I am a loyal ally, a best friend, and a good listener. Family is forever and friends are considered family as well. I volunteer coaching soccer (love it!), teaching Sunday School and Girl Scouts. I love all animals and have cried at dog food commercials and even the spiders get to live on my porch LOL! Enjoy music especially if it’s loud! I am content but looking forward to making a new friend and meeting someone faithful and honest…
